---
import DocsLayout from '../../layouts/DocsLayout.astro';
---

<DocsLayout title="Patterns" description="Reusable recipes that compose Groundwork components into service journeys">
  <section class="gw-section">
    <div class="gw-width gw-stack--lg">
      <div class="gw-prose">
        <h1 class="gw-heading-l">Patterns</h1>
        <p>Patterns describe how to assemble Groundwork components to solve a recurring user need. Larger patterns embed a Flow as their interactive demo and test surface.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="gw-grid">
        <article class="gw-card gw-stack">
          <p class="gw-caption">Submitting information</p>
          <h2 class="gw-heading-m"><a class="gw-link" href="/patterns/submit-information/">Help users submit information correctly</a></h2>
          <p class="gw-body--sm">Validate as the user submits, review what they have entered, and confirm the submission.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="gw-card gw-stack">
          <p class="gw-caption">Submitting information</p>
          <h2 class="gw-heading-m"><a class="gw-link" href="/patterns/check-answers/">Help users check their answers</a></h2>
          <p class="gw-body--sm">Let users review and change pre-entered answers before they commit.</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</DocsLayout>
